review_blob: GRAIN BELT PREMIUM IS BY FAR THE BEST BEER BREWED IN MINNESOTA AND ALWAYS WILL BE.  IT WAS THAT WAY WHEN MINNESOTA BREWING WAS DOING IT, AND IT IS STILL THAT WAY NOW THAT SCHELLS IS SOING IT.  GREAT BEER WILL NEVER GET OLD.
FOSTER'S LAGER IS THE BEST LAGER I HAVE EVER HAD.  IT GOES DOWN SMOOTH AND NEVER LETS ME DOWN.
